com.hp.ov.sdk.dto.storage

Class StorageVolume

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hp.ov.sdk.dto.BaseModelResource
      • com.hp.ov.sdk.dto.storage.StorageVolume
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class StorageVolume
extends BaseModelResource
    The StorageVolume data transfer object (DTO) contains the information used to represent a storage volume in the system. It is passed in to the add/update storage volume REST api, as well as the add/update storage volume through java client api.
